cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.NE 

The paper proposes a novel approach for graph-based semi-supervised learning using neural networks. This falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The approach is applied to image datasets, which suggests computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL) could also be relevant sub-categories. Finally, the use of neural networks and optimization techniques suggests neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE) could also be a possible sub-category.
